Source: pg-kazsearch
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cargo, clang
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/darkhanakh/pg-kazsearch

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-kazsearch
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-kazsearch
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Kazakh full-text search extension for PostgreSQL
 pg_kazsearch adds a Kazakh full-text search configuration, dictionary,
 and lexicon-backed stemmer for PostgreSQL 16 through 18.
 The package also installs the bundled tsearch_data lexicon and stopword
 files required by the extension.
